column5: Check out this story and click on the link at the bottom to find out pricing in your area. This is not good, not good at all!!!!  Gas Price Increases!!!!!
That's a good one.  Scary thing is soon enough it may not be a joke!
Since others wrote got me, it didn't get me
I was 1/2 way out the door with jerry cans in hand until I clicked on the link.
Someone forgot to inform the gas companies ts was just a joke, price at the pump went up around 5c overnight
